Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真好  好香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服  我想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学她  坚守住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  你绝不是怪物
